==========================  Equity Case 2158  ==========================

    Goethe pledged to lead / an effort to grant title / but no new Bard
    yet.

========================================================================

Caller:                                 omd
Barred:                                 G.

Judge:                                  woggle
Judgement:                              

========================================================================

History:

Called by omd:                          14 Sep 2008 01:30:06 GMT
Parties informed:                       14 Sep 2008 04:54:48 GMT
Pre-trial phase ended:                  15 Sep 2008 15:12:31 GMT
Assigned to woggle:                     20 Sep 2008 18:56:55 GMT
